t;text&quot;}" data-margin-left="0.5in" data-text-indent="-0.25in" data-margin-bottom="0pt" data-hd-info="0" data-line-height="1.4" data-list-id="97475710" data-list-info="{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;97475710&quot;,&quot;l&quot;:0}"><span>Builds trust by boosting your search rankings</span></li><li class="zw-list zw-paragraph heading0" data-header="0" data-textformat="{&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;11.00&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}" data-margin-left="0.5in" data-text-indent="-0.25in" data-margin-bottom="0pt" data-hd-info="0" data-line-height="1.4" data-list-id="97475710" data-list-info="{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;97475710&quot;,&quot;l&quot;:0}"><span>Improves site speed and user experience</span></li><li class="zw-list zw-paragraph heading0" data-header="0" data-textformat="{&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;11.00&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}" data-margin-left="0.5in" data-text-indent="-0.25in" data-margin-bottom="12pt" data-hd-info="0" data-line-height="1.4" data-list-id="97475710" data-list-info="{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;97475710&quot;,&quot;l&quot;:0}"><span>Connects you with real leads already searching for your services</span></li></ul><p data-pm-slice="0 0 []">We’re not just any agency; we’re a trusted search engine optimization agency, and with 68% of online experiences starting with a search engine (BrightEdge), we know exactly where to focus.</p>								</div>
